{"type": "article", "id": 63496, "title": "用过期鸡蛋做的餐具，破碎的蛋壳也是漂亮的纹理｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-05-04T22:47:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 58339, "name": "Doconomy"}, {"id": 16699, "name": "RIMOWA"}, {"id": 58340, "name": "Bowers & Wilkins"}, {"id": 58341, "name": "Brana Studio"}, {"id": 58342, "name": "Pampa"}, {"id": 18566, "name": "Daniel Arsham"}, {"id": 58343, "name": "Basse Stittgen"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190504230707YRbpUnFWDXyzecuZ.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} </style>  </p><h3>How You You Like Your Eggs？by Basse Stittgen </h3><p>德国设计师 Basse Stittgen 意在通过一系列仅由过期鸡蛋制成的餐具来解决全球食物浪费和过度消费的问题。</p><p>这是他的项目“How You You Like Your Eggs？”的一部分，Basse Stittgen 希望能够探索常见物品的不同属性，比如各种废弃物。</p><p>设计师将废弃的鸡蛋变成了一系列金色的生物塑料蛋杯和碟子，破碎的蛋壳图案成了天然的纹理图案。</p><p>Stittgen 首先收集当地面包店剩余的鸡蛋，然后将其分解成蛋清、蛋黄和蛋壳。将蛋清脱水并研磨成粉末，同时将蛋壳压碎成小块，将这两种元素混合在一起并放入铝模具中，然后在 200 度下高温压制而成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230750re75fqwjPylN4snG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.840525\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905042307502KWeAH6u8t3ECfrO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.765228\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230752xORjAZk1wH4ast9q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905042307505kh0tfLFHUJDY6WM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230753swNfYALZyTHgjWXv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734349\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230851IhQHjn1guZidky8E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905042308519lH5AWZCcgkDuTKi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230852R4b0WBiMmUIh5gPS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734349\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Porteño Folka chair, Porteño swinging chair, and Porteño swing by Brana Studio for Pampa</h3><p>Pampa 是位于澳洲拜伦湾的家居用品品牌，其成立的目的是为下一代保护编织手工艺。在盖丘亚语中， Pampa 的意思是“位于山间的平原”，其产品也反映出一种根深蒂固的本土气息。</p><p>最近，Pampa 与 Brana Studio 的阿根廷设计师合作推出了三款新椅子，包括现代风格的 Porteño Folka 椅子，俏皮的 Porteño 摇椅和经典的 Porteño 秋千。</p><p>每件作品均采用原生木材和优质天然植鞣原皮制作，保留了 Pampa 与 Brana Studio 对于传统工艺的热爱。所使用的原材料均是来自布宜诺斯艾利斯南部的 Las Pampas 地区。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230917xWZgA0NFiEqtX3hn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230917qtsFbOTJlCZaSPi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230918lTL1rNWSwEfI3ZxB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230918Gdj3eq7aRvFC9JM5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230919RxO6lXhZy81vDmjK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905042309195jqo4Ul3MyaPEtbh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230919k6ij7sWxFGEylJ9p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230920tVQD8XCdfLFJnj3r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504230920lwrOLaxqbJcUHPXe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635938\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://pampa.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">pampa</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Formation Suite by Bowers &amp; Wilkins</h3><p>美国音响品牌 Bowers &amp; Wilkins 推出最新的 Formation 系列无线音箱，试图在提供给用户无线便利的同时也提供有线音箱般的发烧级音质。</p><p>Bowers &amp; Wilkins Formation 系列由五个产品组成，分别是立体声书架箱 Formation Duo、单个异形箱 Formation Wedge、超低音音箱 Formation Bass、电视音响棒 Formation Bar 及无线音频转换器 Formation Audio。</p><p>全系列产品支持 24bit/96kHz 超高分辨率并且支持由 Bowers &amp; Wilkins 母公司 EVA Automation 研发的网状网络无线连接技术，它能让无线音箱以 1 微秒的延迟同步音频。</p><p>对于无线音箱来说，延迟是非常敏感的一个技术指标，这个延迟包括手机或任何无线音频源从点击播放到音箱开始播放音乐的响应时间及音箱间的音乐同步，而 Bowers &amp; Wilkins 独家的网状网络连接技术就允许他们的任意两个 Formation 喇叭间的音乐同步延迟只有 1 微秒。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231047rEHg1apGNqxZbn0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652344\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231048SRahv4OIfH9DL702.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231049FmHYDu9asgj4ZQB6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.773438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231049pC6gBIadMYEFKJUZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231050LgEOvNSWs8ozFtMZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231051IUFm9EbulBqWe2rK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231051XxQtq2Zr5m48NFwy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905042310472tbFxkfV7TIKBXrN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231052ipnEZq9hI4AF3UH2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677344\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.bowerswilkins.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bowers &amp; Wilkins</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The limited-edition piece by Daniel Arsham for RIMOWA</h3><p>高端箱包品牌 RIMOWA 最近与纽约知名艺术家 Daniel Arsham 合作，根据后者的 Future Relic 风格，共同创作了一件行李箱雕塑作品。</p><p>Daniel Arsham 雕塑的侵蚀美学，使这件作品看起来像是从考古遗迹的碎片中挖掘出来一般。打开这只已经失去光泽的 RIMOWA 铝制行李箱之后，展现的内容是 Arsham Studio 的专用手套和说明手册，还有那只像考古文物的行李箱雕塑，并且每件作品都有编号。在 5 月 2 日至 13 日期间，Sotheby’s 将会在网上对一件独一无二的特殊版本进行拍卖，除了这件作品本身，还将包括签名的绘画稿件、一封来自 Arsham 的信、一组特别的贴纸。之后，这个作品会 5 月 17 日上架 RIMOWA 官网和 Daniel Arsham 官网，售价 2200 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231231JcLZpvNXkrPExOMB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231231zB04D2woxfOResZk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231231Oga9McWGthAVS6z8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231231ajcANI6FWHZpdryC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231232MYWrBX5xhUgi6C1Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231232HhVkUJTAj0x9oluF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231232SHknzjlm7qVJaQ0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231232PNHOkq7r8x2hiCvn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>DO Black credit card by Doconomy</h3><p>瑞典金融科技公司 Doconomy 推出了一张信用卡，用于跟踪用户购买的二氧化碳排放量。</p><p>这款 DO Black 信用卡直接将我们的消费与其对地球的影响联系起来，以鼓励我们每天减少碳足迹。用户可以使用 DO 卡进行日常购物，通过 DO 应用程序跟踪与其消费相关的碳排放。DO 应用程序使用一个名为 Åland Index 的计算系统来衡量每笔交易产生的二氧化碳，并允许用户限制其支出对气候的影响。</p><p>那些注册 DO 的人将获得免费储蓄账户，帮助他们了解他们的碳足迹，了解联合国认证的气候补偿项目，并发现对人类和地球产生积极影响的投资基金。</p><p>卡片本身由生物材料制成，并印有一种由回收的空气污染颗粒制成的墨水。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231404C9ihvN1fyALGMxEg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.809645\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231404RmxjltMaYSpKAiTd.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231405D5LSyb1TE4iowCGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.969543\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190504231405aVDlj7wLQvURyn2c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.222081\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/05/03/doconomy-climate-change-credit-card/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>"}